title: Zach Wilson and the Jets Stall Against the Patriots Once Again
description: Wilson threw three puzzling interceptions, and the Jets lost an early lead. New England has won the past 13 regular-season meetings.
dc:creator: Jenny Vrentas
media:credit: Brad Penner/USA Today Sports, via Reuters
media:description: Jets quarterback Zach Wilson forced Patriots safety Devin McCourty out of bounds after McCourty intercepted him for the second time on Sunday.
